#: course/lesson-13-conditions/lesson.bbcode:5
msgid "In previous lessons, we decreased and increased a character's health, but there was no limit to how much health they could have."
msgstr ""

#: course/lesson-13-conditions/lesson.bbcode:9
msgid "As a result, the player could increase their character's health indefinitely, which we do not want."
msgstr ""

#: course/lesson-13-conditions/lesson.bbcode:11
#. TRANSLATORS: Quiz question
msgid "What happens to health when we damage our character?"
msgstr ""

#: course/lesson-13-conditions/lesson.bbcode:11
#. TRANSLATORS: Quiz content
